		"Details": "The Hu Tao is a modernization of the old Ignis infantry support vehicle, intended to form an armored spearhead with battle armor squads in urban environments. The anime girl decals and cheery funeral home advertisements adorning a typical specimen of this type go poorly with the screams of unprotected persons caught in its flamethrowers.\n<color=#87CEEB>[More Vehicles]</color>\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>CARRIES A SQUAD OF YING LONG BATTLE ARMOR!</color></b>\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Tracked: High traction, agile turning.</color></b>\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 5/8 Hex: 150/240 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<b>Armor:</b> Heavy Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>        260     20\n<b>Left</b>          130     20\n<b>Right</b>        130     20\n<b>Rear</b>         90     20\n<b>Turret</b>       130     20\n\n<b>Total</b>      740     100\n",
